OL,3,CUK researchers work to save one of the
OL,4,Cworld's most beautiful snails
OL,6,FUK scientists are working to save one
OL,7,Fof the world's most beautiful snails
OL,8,Fwhich is at risk of extinction due to
OL,9,Fthe popularity of their striking
OL,10,Fshells.
OL,12,FThe snails, known as Polymita, are
OL,13,Fendemic to Eastern Cuba and feature
OL,14,Fshells with vibrant colours and
OL,15,Finteresting patterns.
OL,17,FThe shells come in many different
OL,18,Fcolours, from yellow and pink to red
OL,19,Fand black.
