OL,3,CUK researchers work to save one of the
OL,4,Cworld's most beautiful snails
OL,6,FBut these patterned shells have become
OL,7,Fpopular among collectors and poachers
OL,8,Fwho sell the shells to tourists or
OL,9,Ftrade them overseas.
OL,11,FDespite it being illegal to remove
OL,12,Fthese snails from their native habitat
OL,13,Funder the Convention on International
OL,14,FTrade in Endangered Species, it has
OL,15,Fnot stopped the international trade of
OL,16,Fthe shells.
