OL,3,CUK researchers work to save one of the
OL,4,Cworld's most beautiful snails
OL,6,FResearchers from London Zoo and the
OL,7,FUniversity of Nottingham have
OL,8,Ftravelled to Cuba to meet local
OL,9,Fscientists to assess the conservation
OL,10,Fstatus of the six vulnerable painted
OL,11,Fsnails, as well as better understand
OL,12,Ftheir evolution and how to breed them.
OL,14,FThe Polymita sulphurosa snail, which
OL,15,Fhas a lime green, blue and yellow
OL,16,Fshell, is considered the most
OL,17,Fendangered of the species and is at
OL,18,Frisk of extinction.
