OL,3,CUK researchers work to save one of the
OL,4,Cworld's most beautiful snails
OL,6,FThere are believed to be fewer than
OL,7,F30,000 remaining in the coastal
OL,8,Fforests of Cuba, which is the only
OL,9,Fplace they live.
OL,11,FUniversity of Nottingham's Professor
OL,12,Fof Evolutionary Genetics Angus Davison
OL,13,Fis hoping to get the species put on
OL,14,Fthe International Union for
OL,15,FConservation of Nature's red list.
OL,17,F"It's all part of a global effort to
OL,18,Fbe proactive about the species
OL,19,Fconservation," Professor Davison said.
