OL,3,CUK researchers work to save one of the
OL,4,Cworld's most beautiful snails
OL,6,F"One species of painted snail is the
OL,7,Fmost threatened ` it was touch and go,
OL,8,Fbut we were very fortunate to finally
OL,9,Ffind them."
OL,11,FThe experts also hope to establish a
OL,12,Fconservation breeding programme in a
OL,13,Flab to help save the invertebrate from
OL,14,Fextinction.
