OL,3,CUK researchers work to save one of the
OL,4,Cworld's most beautiful snails
OL,6,FLondon Zoo's Dave Clarke said the
OL,7,FCuban painted snails were "incredible"
OL,8,Fand he was very keen to conserve the
OL,9,Fspecies.
OL,11,F"Finally finding a population of the
OL,12,Frarest species in a remote location
OL,13,Fwas a relief, however we also saw
OL,14,Fevidence of fresh habitat
OL,15,Fdestruction," he said.
OL,17,F"We hope these exceptional snails can
OL,18,Fbe successfully reared in the lab to
OL,19,Flearn more about them and provide a
OL,20,Ffailsafe against the threats in the
OL,21,Fwild."
